modName: LaBeats unobtrusive tree LODs for enb
summary: Im not much of a modder, but one single thing in this game was bugging me so much, that I just had to fix it myself.
descriptionHtml:
Tree LODs
I tried lot of things, downloading mods that were supposed to fix the uglyness of the tree lods, fiddled with the skyrim inis to push them further into the distance - nothing helped. 

One day, I had enough. And I decided to finally fix this. I spend 5 minutes to photoshop the tree lods so they blend in seamlessly. 

Tested with my current enb ( mure enb ) should work for other enbs as well




I am not a modder, this is my first "mod" other than enbs, so I guess the best way to install this one it to replace the file manually. 
Look up the readme tab for instructions


REMEMBER TO ALLWAYS BACK UP YOUR FILES




Permissions and further use:
The upload is hereby free to be used and modified for further usage as resource, no credit required.

I literally just spend 5 minutes ( or less ) to modify the original tree lods
